full_text: A special grand jury in Fulton County, Ga., is subpoenaing Rudy Giuliani and other advisers to former President Donald Trump, representing a new development in a Democratic county prosecutor’s investigation into efforts to overturn Georgia’s 2020 election https://t.co/Fy5PduwLrH
